description:
Welcome to this one owner and rare North Central Desert Hills custom home and property! Situated on 2.7 acres, this custom-built 2002 Santa Fe territorial home has three bedrooms and two bathrooms in  a spacious 1,775 square feet single story home. 

Step inside to discover an exceptional interior featuring abundant custom kitchen cabinetry, a cozy gas fireplace, and dedicated office space. The private gate entrance directly off Central Avenue leads you down past the arena and mare motel.

 For equine enthusiasts, this property includes a 45' x 25' 4-stall mare motel, with each stall measuring 12' x 16', alongside a sprawling 110' x 225' arena/turnout. 

Maneuvering is made easy with a separate pull-through exit and ample space to maneuver your horse trailer. Imagine waking up and enjoying your morning rides with access to thousands of acres of State Trust Land, just a short distance away, or working from home while watching your horses in the arena from the office.

description: Gorgeous open concept single level split floor plan. Upgrades over the past year include interior & exterior paint, carpet, double oven, dishwasher, microwave, washer/dryer, window treatments, pool surface, and water softener... it's move-in ready!!! Generous family room opens directly to the chef's gourmet kitchen boasting those new appliances, five burner gas cooktop, slab granite countertops with large island, and rich cherry wood cabinetry. Abundant upgrades include central vacuum with kitchen crumb sweep, surround sound, garage storage, large format tile flooring, dual master bath vanities, separate shower and soaking tub, and large walk in closet. Paradise resort oasis backyard is very private, offering plenty of covered & sun patios surrounding the sparkling play pool equipped ... with in floor cleaning, water feature, and energy efficient variable speed pool pump. 3 car garage! With this much pride of ownership, it's a gem that won't last!

description: Charming 4 bedroom, 2 bath home with north/south exposure on large cul-de-sac lot. Enter the paved front courtyard and double front door to a lovely great room floor plan with pretty tile floors and stone fireplace. Kitchen has granite counters and stainless appliances.  Brand new carpet in bedrooms. Master bedroom is split from other bedrooms and features a walk-in closet, updated master bathroom with double sinks, tiled shower plus a sliding door to back patio. Additional 3 bedrooms are spacious and share the updated secondary bathroom with an tile shower and granite counter. Upgraded dual pane windows. Backyard has a large shady covered wrap around back patio with plenty of seating areas and a handy pass through window from kitchen. Sparkling fenced diving pool completes the backyard.
